{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"joinedAt":2026.0,"programName":"USER_GROUP_LEADER"},{"category":"Community Hero","joinedAt":2019.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"antonbabenko","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/3DdkVXzqcvfhbEF48P8g2hG4IoR.webp","bio":"Anton is a long-time developer and CTO. He runs a consulting company Betajob in Norway and has helped companies around the globe build solutions using AWS and specializing in Infrastructure-as-Code, DevOps, and reusable infrastructure components since 2015. Through his consulting and ongoing experimentation with new technologies, Anton also created compliance.tf, a product that helps companies in regulated industries simplify and automate compliance when using Terraform.\n\nHe spends much of his time as an open-source contributor on various Terraform & AWS projects. Such as Terraform AWS modules (provisioned more than 2 billion times), Terraform best practices ebook (https://www.terraform-best-practices.com/), Serverless Terraform framework (https://serverless.tf), Terraform Weekly newsletter (https://weekly.tf), Your Weekly Dose of Terraform live streams (https://www.youtube.com/AntonBabenkoLive), and more (https://github.com/antonbabenko/terraform-aws-devops).\n\nAnton enjoys solving current cloud architecture tasks, figuring out generic solutions by getting to the core, and making them available as open-source to benefit the AWS community.\n\nAnton co-founded and co-organizes AWS, DevOps, and HashiCorp User Groups in Oslo (Norway) and often speaks at technical meetups and conferences.","builderProfileId":"1e84cf67-9f07-46fd-a741-0c965cd7509a","createdOn":1.711051374592E12,"headline":"Terraform AWS fanatic","isStaff":false,"name":"Anton Babenko"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"NO"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/antonbabenko","linkedIn":"https://linkedin.com/in/antonbabenko","personal":"https://compliance.tf","twitter":"https://twitter.com/antonbabenko","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGH0yYPvlCN1VjSFMGVmFgQ"}}}